from zander mark zander subject re modem and noisy line i use to have a lot of line noise problem with my baud modem what wa sudgested to me wa to put a toriod transformer on the line thi be easily do by get a large toroid core from ymy local electronic shop a toroid core be a donut and wind the telephone line in through the center of the core and out around the outside five or six time thi be a easy and cheap fix that do not have the hassel of have to use sofware to fix a hardware problem talk to yah later mark 